### Problem11

Please finish the form below to convert between binary number to decimal number.

|   Binary    |Decimal |
|  :---:  | :---: |
|    100        | _____(0)\___ |
|    1001        | _____(1)\___|
|    01101       | _____(2)\___|
|_____(3)\___      |   37|
|_____(4)\___      |   156|
